<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 18" captionStartId="F20" captionText="Figure 18. Radula, Peronia okinawensis, Japan, Okinawa A, B holotype [696 - 4 H] (UF 352288) C-F [696 - 2] (UF 352288) A left half rows of teeth B rachidian and innermost lateral teeth C rachidian and innermost lateral teeth D rachidian and lateral teeth E lateral teeth F outermost lateral teeth. Scale bars: 200 μm (A), 80 μm (B), 20 μm (C, F), 60 μm (D), 100 μm (E)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.972.52853.figure18" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/458318" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">18</figureCitation>
