<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
long. The hook of the lateral teeth is approximately 110 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
long. The intestinal loops are of type I, with a transitional loop oriented between 12 to 3 
<normalizedToken originalValue="o’clock">o'clock</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
